<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/national-protective-security-authority> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "National Protective Security Authority (NPSA) is the UK’s National Technical Authority for physical and personnel protective security, working to make the UK less vulnerable and more resilient to national security threats. NPSA is part of The Security Service ."@en .
